name: Harvest Balanced Income & Growth ETF
longDescription: Fund investing, on a non-levered basis, in a portfolio of exchange traded funds that are listed on a recognized North American stock exchange that provide exposure towards large capitalization equity securities, investment grade bonds or money market instruments issued by corporations or governments, and will include exchange traded funds that engage in covered call strategies. Harvest Balanced Income  Growth ETF will seek to provide Unitholders with high monthly cash distributions and the opportunity for capital appreciation.
